    whyCallUs: "Flagstaff homeowners call us in January at 11 p.m. because no one else answers. Freeze emergencies do not happen on business hours, and a frozen pipe that bursts while you are asleep can flood a room in 20 minutes. We staff winter emergency coverage for Flagstaff specifically because we know the risk is real and the alternatives are few. We are an AZ ROC-licensed plumbing contractor — licensed, bonded, and insured. Verify us at roc.az.gov. Mike the owner takes quality-control calls personally. We quote the repair in writing before any pipe is cut.",
